Its quite challenging, given that both of them are extremely heavy workload classes with lot of theoretical material and long psets every week.

However, depending on your mathematical background (in preparation for 189 such as EE 126/127/16AB/Math 53/110) and what your other classes/commitments would be, this could definitely be manageable.
